tutorialPages.messageText: NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "6645CF2342DDCF6732284A8F9A19C54D", "Congratulations, you leveled up your first Gathering Profession! As you level up you\'ll be able to apply for higher certification ranks.")

NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "576556EE483C2823829CDE9B47A6B51B", "At level 10 you can apply for your first Certification level: Apprentice. This will give you access to better gear, stronger tools, and higher quality resources.")
